        {
            "decision": "No obstructing lesion is identified.  The patient is status post cholecystectomy.  The pancreas, spleen, and adrenal glands are unremarkable.  There are bilateral circumscribed hypodense lesions in the kidneys consistent with cysts.  Almost all of these are too small to accurately characterize by CT.  No lymphadenopathy is apparent.",
