        {
            "decision": "THERE IS AN ADJACENT SHORT LOOP OF ABNORMAL SMALL BOWEL.  ITS ENHANCEMENT SUGGESTS POSSIBLE INVASION BY TUMOR AND THERE [**Month (only) **] BE ACTIVE BLEEDING AT THIS SITE",
